4 nginx的几个默认目录

输入命令: whereis nginx

nginx: /usr/sbin/nginx /etc/nginx /usr/share/nginx

1) 配置所在目录：/etc/nginx/

2) PID目录：/var/run/nginx.pid

3) 错误日志：/var/log/nginx/error.log

4) 访问日志：/var/log/nginx/access.log

5) 默认站点目录：/usr/share/nginx/html

5 常用命令

1) 启动nginx：nginx

2) 重启nginx：killall -HUP nginx

3) 测试nginx配置：nginx -t
netstat -lnp|grep 88
